---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = '/tradfi-onchain';
---

<Layout title="Family Offices — Crypto Allocation Guide">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-24">
    <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">
      <span class="lang-en">Family Offices</span><span class="lang-zh">家族辦公室</span>
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
      <span class="lang-en">HK Family Office Crypto Allocation Guide</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">香港家族辦公室加密資產配置指南</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
      <span class="lang-en">How Hong Kong family offices are increasing digital asset allocations following the February 2026 tax concession that put crypto on the same footing as equities and bonds.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">2026年2月稅務優惠將數字資產與股票債券同等對待後，香港家族辦公室如何增加加密資產配置。</span>
    </p>

    <!-- Stats grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-12">
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">28%</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">HK FOs increasing crypto</span><span class="lang-zh">香港家辦增加加密配置</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">3,380+</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">HK single-family offices</span><span class="lang-zh">香港單一家族辦公室</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Feb 2026</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Digital asset tax concession</span><span class="lang-zh">數字資產稅務優惠</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">220+</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">New FO target 2026-28</span><span class="lang-zh">2026-28新家辦目標</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-zinc max-w-none text-zinc-400 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-6">

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">In March 2026, the Hong Kong Institute for Monetary and Financial Research published a survey of 101 family office entities operating in Hong Kong. The findings were striking: 28% plan to increase their digital asset allocations over the next three years, while only 1% plan to decrease — the widest increase-to-decrease gap of any asset class in the survey. Among the 3,380-plus single-family offices now operating in Hong Kong (a 25% increase over two years), digital assets have moved from a curiosity to a serious allocation conversation.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">2026年3月，香港金融研究院發表了一項針對101間在港運營的家族辦公室實體的調查。調查結果引人注目：28%計劃在未來三年增加數字資產配置，而僅1%計劃減少 — 這是調查中所有資產類別中增減差距最大的。在香港現有的3,380多間單一家族辦公室（兩年內增長25%）中，數字資產已從一種好奇事物發展為一個嚴肅的配置話題。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">What changed? In February 2026, the Hong Kong government added digital assets to the list of qualifying investments under the family office tax concession regime. The implications are significant.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">什麼改變了？2026年2月，香港政府將數字資產加入家族辦公室稅務優惠制度下的合資格投資名單。其影響是重大的。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">The Tax Concession: Before and After</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">稅務優惠：前後對比</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Before February 2026, digital assets were not listed as qualifying investments. Family offices that wanted to allocate to crypto had to independently evaluate the tax treatment — engaging external counsel, navigating ambiguity, and accepting uncertainty about whether profits would be tax-exempt. The legal costs alone deterred many offices from exploring the space, even those with a strategic interest.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">2026年2月之前，數字資產未被列入合資格投資名單。希望配置加密資產的家族辦公室必須自行評估稅務處理 — 聘請外部律師、在模糊中摸索、並接受利潤是否免稅的不確定性。僅法律成本就令許多辦公室望而卻步，即使它們有戰略興趣。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Now the policy is explicit. Digital assets qualify for profits tax exemption under the same regime as equities, bonds, and other traditional investments held through qualifying family-owned investment holding vehicles. The tax treatment is consistent with traditional assets. For family offices structured to meet the substantial activity requirements in Hong Kong, the path is clear.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">現在政策是明確的。數字資產在與股票、債券及其他傳統投資相同的制度下享有利得稅豁免，前提是通過合資格的家族所有投資控股載體持有。稅務處理與傳統資產一致。對於按照香港實質活動要求構建的家族辦公室，路徑是清晰的。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The government's target is to assist 220 or more family offices to establish or expand in Hong Kong between 2026 and 2028 — and the digital asset tax concession is explicitly part of the pitch to attract them.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">政府的目標是在2026至2028年間協助220間以上家族辦公室在香港設立或擴展 — 而數字資產稅務優惠明確是吸引它們的策略之一。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Three Allocation Tiers</span><span class="lang-zh">三個配置層級</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Conservative: tokenized Treasuries.</span> BlackRock's BUIDL ($2.4 billion AUM) and Franklin Templeton's BENJI ($742 million AUM) are tokenized US government money market funds — the same underlying assets as a traditional money market fund, yielding roughly 4.5% annualized, available onchain with real-time NAV and 24/7 redemption. The only additional risk beyond US government credit risk is smart contract exposure. For first-time allocators with fiduciary obligations, these are familiar names with auditable track records.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">保守：代幣化美債。</span>BlackRock的BUIDL（$24億AUM）和Franklin Templeton的BENJI（$7.42億AUM）是代幣化美國政府貨幣市場基金 — 底層資產與傳統貨幣市場基金相同，年化收益約4.5%，在鏈上提供實時資產淨值和24/7贖回。除美國政府信用風險外，唯一額外風險是智能合約敞口。對於有受託義務的首次配置者，這些是熟悉的品牌，有可審計的業績記錄。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Moderate: core holdings plus staking yield.</span> BTC and ETH purchased through licensed VATPs (HashKey, OSL) sit within a regulated custody framework. ETH staking — approved by the SFC for licensed platforms in April 2025 — generates roughly 3 to 4% APR on top of any price appreciation. This is now a regulated crypto yield product in Hong Kong, not a gray area. Liquid staking tokens allow continued capital deployment while earning staking rewards.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">穩健：核心持倉加質押收益。</span>通過持牌VATP（HashKey、OSL）購買的BTC和ETH位於受監管的託管框架內。ETH質押 — SFC於2025年4月批准持牌平台提供 — 在任何價格升值之上產生約3至4%年化收益。這在香港現在是受監管的加密收益產品，而非灰色地帶。流動質押代幣允許在賺取質押獎勵的同時繼續部署資金。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Growth: DeFi yield and active strategies.</span> Stablecoin lending on Aave or Morpho (3 to 8% APR), liquidity provision on AMMs, pre-IPO valuation exposure via Hyperliquid HIP-3 perps (SpaceX, OpenAI, Anthropic), and 24/7 commodity perps (WTI crude, Brent, gold, silver, natural gas) for weekend gap coverage on energy and metals positions. These strategies carry meaningful smart contract risk, oracle risk, and counterparty risk — and they are not regulated by the SFC. They are appropriate only for offices with crypto-experienced staff or a dedicated digital asset mandate, and with capital they can afford to lose entirely.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">增長：DeFi收益與主動策略。</span>在Aave或Morpho上進行穩定幣借貸（3至8%年化）、在AMM上提供流動性、通過Hyperliquid HIP-3永續合約獲取Pre-IPO估值敞口（SpaceX、OpenAI、Anthropic），以及24/7商品永續合約（WTI原油、布倫特、黃金、白銀、天然氣）為能源同金屬倉位提供週末gap coverage。這些策略帶有顯著的智能合約風險、預言機風險和對手方風險 — 且不受SFC監管。它們僅適合擁有加密經驗人員或專門數字資產授權的辦公室，且使用可完全承受損失的資金。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Practical Considerations</span><span class="lang-zh">實務考量</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Custody.</span> Licensed VATPs provide SFC-regulated custody with 98%+ cold storage requirements and mandatory insurance. For larger allocations, dedicated institutional custodians like Hex Trust and Anchorage Digital offer insurance-backed cold storage with multi-signature controls. The upcoming VA custodian licensing regime in 2026 will expand the regulated custody options available.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">託管。</span>持牌VATP提供SFC監管的託管服務，要求98%以上冷存儲和強制保險。對於較大配置，Hex Trust和Anchorage Digital等專門機構託管人提供有保險支持的冷存儲和多重簽名控制。2026年即將推出的VA託管人牌照制度將擴大可用的受監管託管選擇。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Compliance and reporting.</span> Onchain assets provide inherently verifiable audit trails — every transaction is recorded on a public ledger. NAV tracking is real-time. Work with your tax advisor to ensure that digital asset investments are structured correctly under the family office tax concession regime; the February 2026 amendment provides clear guidance, but the specific vehicle structuring to meet substantial activity requirements will vary by office.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">合規與報告。</span>鏈上資產提供固有的可驗證審計軌跡 — 每筆交易都記錄在公共賬本上。資產淨值跟蹤實時進行。與你的稅務顧問合作，確保數字資產投資在家族辦公室稅務優惠制度下正確結構化；2026年2月修訂提供了明確指引，但滿足實質活動要求的具體載體結構因辦公室而異。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The HKIMR data tells a clear story: the family offices that are already here — 3,380 and growing — are moving toward digital assets, not away from them. The tax concession removed the last major institutional barrier. What remains is execution: choosing the right products, setting up custody, and sizing the allocation appropriately for your mandate.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">HKIMR的數據講述了一個清晰的故事：已經在這裡的家族辦公室 — 3,380間且持續增長 — 正在向數字資產靠攏，而非遠離。稅務優惠消除了最後一個主要機構障礙。剩下的是執行：選擇合適的產品、設立託管、以及根據你的授權適當調整配置規模。</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="mt-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-950/30 to-zinc-900/50 border border-green-900/30 rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Evaluating crypto allocation for your family office?</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">為你的家族辦公室評估加密資產配置？</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">We provide guidance on products, custody, and tax structuring for HK family offices.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">我們為香港家族辦公室提供產品、託管及稅務結構方面的指導。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <a href="https://wa.me/85256171671" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-green-500 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-green-400 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
        WhatsApp
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 flex justify-between">
      <a href={`${base}/apply/asset-management`} class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">
        <span class="lang-en">← Asset Management</span><span class="lang-zh">← 資產管理</span>
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}/apply/prop-trading`} class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">
        <span class="lang-en">Prop Trading →</span><span class="lang-zh">自營交易 →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
